the Water, and fill tho&s;e Ponds or Ci&s;terns, &s;o that it is di&s;tributed throughout all the City. I ought not to forget to mention the Fountains of <HI>Ausbourg,</HI> which are one of its principal Ornaments. There are many of them which are almo&s;t as magni|ficent as the fine Fountain at <HI>Nuremberg.</HI></P>
